name: RytinaCleaners
0:
”Alexa, open Rytina Cleaners.”
”Alexa, tell Rytina Cleaners that I am on my way.”
”Alexa, ask Rytina Cleaners to pick up my clothes.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rytina cleaners
Developer Terms of Use
des: Dry cleaning and laundry has never been easier! Simply have Alexa tell Rytina Cleaners that "I'm on my way" and all of your clothes will be pulled, ready and waiting for you when you come in. You can even ask to have Rytina Cleaners schedule a free route pick up and Alexa will let you know when next your driver will be by. The Rytina Alexa skill is indeed the easiest way to dry clean.
